---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" activeNav="services">

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <span class="section-label">What I Offer</span>
      <h1>Services for Senior Leaders</h1>
      <p>
        Every engagement is designed around your specific situation, not a template.
        Here&rsquo;s how most leaders find their way in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="services-body">

    <!-- 1: Strategic Advisory -->
    <section class="service-block" id="strategy">
      <div class="service-block-inner">
        <div class="service-block-text">
          <span class="section-label">Service 01</span>
          <h2>Strategic Advisory</h2>
          <p>
            An ongoing thinking partnership designed for executives who need a trusted
            outside voice. We meet regularly to examine your strategy, challenge
            assumptions, and stress-test decisions before they become commitments.
          </p>
          <p>
            This isn&rsquo;t consulting &mdash; it&rsquo;s a relationship. You bring the real
            questions, I bring structured frameworks, pattern recognition across industries,
            and the candor that internal stakeholders rarely offer.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Monthly or bi-weekly advisory sessions</li>
            <li>Between-session availability via async messaging</li>
            <li>Annual strategy review and scenario planning</li>
            <li>Board prep and investor narrative coaching</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-teal">Start a Conversation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-block-visual">
          <div class="service-visual-card">
            <div class="svc-icon">&#9654;</div>
            <h3>Who This Is For</h3>
            <p>CEOs, COOs, and senior leaders navigating growth, transition, or sustained complexity who need a thinking partner outside the org chart.</p>
            <div class="svc-divider"></div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Format</span>
              <span>Monthly retainer</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Cadence</span>
              <span>2&ndash;4 sessions/month</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Commitment</span>
              <span>3-month minimum</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2: Executive Coaching (reversed) -->
    <section class="service-block reverse" id="executive">
      <div class="service-block-inner">
        <div class="service-block-text">
          <span class="section-label">Service 02</span>
          <h2>Executive Coaching</h2>
          <p>
            Leadership at the top is a uniquely isolating experience. One-on-one coaching
            creates a private space to develop your leadership edge &mdash; how you show up,
            how you decide, and how you influence without authority.
          </p>
          <p>
            We work on the intersection of mindset, behavior, and organizational dynamics.
            This isn&rsquo;t therapy, it&rsquo;s professional excellence work grounded in real
            challenges you face every week.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Bi-weekly 1:1 coaching sessions</li>
            <li>360&deg; leadership assessment and debrief</li>
            <li>Real-time support during high-stakes moments</li>
            <li>Leadership narrative and presence development</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-teal">Start a Conversation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-block-visual">
          <div class="service-visual-card">
            <div class="svc-icon">&#9670;</div>
            <h3>Who This Is For</h3>
            <p>Senior leaders transitioning into expanded roles, newly promoted executives, or experienced leaders who want to operate at a higher level.</p>
            <div class="svc-divider"></div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Format</span>
              <span>Monthly retainer</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Cadence</span>
              <span>Bi-weekly sessions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Commitment</span>
              <span>6-month engagement</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3: Team Alignment -->
    <section class="service-block" id="team">
      <div class="service-block-inner">
        <div class="service-block-text">
          <span class="section-label">Service 03</span>
          <h2>Team Alignment</h2>
          <p>
            When leadership teams aren&rsquo;t aligned, the whole organization feels it.
            Facilitated working sessions and offsites that cut through surface-level
            consensus to get at what&rsquo;s actually true &mdash; and build genuine shared direction.
          </p>
          <p>
            I design and facilitate sessions that create real movement: clearer priorities,
            resolved tensions, sharper accountability, and a team that actually trusts
            each other to deliver.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Half-day and full-day facilitated sessions</li>
            <li>Pre-session discovery and stakeholder interviews</li>
            <li>Post-session action planning and accountability</li>
            <li>Follow-on check-ins at 30 and 90 days</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-teal">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-block-visual">
          <div class="service-visual-card">
            <div class="svc-icon">&#9632;</div>
            <h3>Who This Is For</h3>
            <p>Leadership teams preparing for a strategic pivot, post-merger integration, or any moment when alignment is critical and hard to achieve internally.</p>
            <div class="svc-divider"></div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Format</span>
              <span>Project-based</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Duration</span>
              <span>1&ndash;3 day sessions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Prep time</span>
              <span>2&ndash;4 weeks</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4: Lunch & Learns (reversed) -->
    <section class="service-block reverse" id="lunch">
      <div class="service-block-inner">
        <div class="service-block-text">
          <span class="section-label">Service 04</span>
          <h2>Lunch &amp; Learns</h2>
          <p>
            Practical, engaging sessions that give your leadership team new frameworks
            and sharper tools for the work they&rsquo;re already doing. Not theoretical &mdash;
            these are working sessions grounded in the real challenges your organization faces.
          </p>
          <p>
            Topics are tailored to your team&rsquo;s current priorities. Past sessions have
            covered strategic communication, leading through ambiguity, executive decision
            frameworks, and organizational influence.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>90-minute to half-day sessions</li>
            <li>Customized to your team&rsquo;s priorities</li>
            <li>Interactive format &mdash; not a lecture</li>
            <li>Follow-up resource pack included</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-teal">Request a Session</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-block-visual">
          <div class="service-visual-card">
            <div class="svc-icon">&#9711;</div>
            <h3>Who This Is For</h3>
            <p>Teams at any level who need a structured, expert-led conversation around leadership, strategy, or organizational effectiveness &mdash; without a multi-month commitment.</p>
            <div class="svc-divider"></div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Format</span>
              <span>Flat-fee session</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Duration</span>
              <span>90 min &ndash; 4 hours</span>
            </div>
            <div class="svc-detail">
              <span class="svc-detail-label">Team size</span>
              <span>5&ndash;40 participants</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="cta-band-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Next Step</span>
      <h2>Not Sure Which Fits? Let&rsquo;s Talk.</h2>
      <p>
        A 30-minute call is enough to figure out where you are, where you want to be,
        and whether we&rsquo;re the right fit.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/work-with-me" class="btn-white">Book a Call</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">Send a Message</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .services-body {
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .service-block {
    padding: 96px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,58,95,0.07);
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .service-block:nth-child(even) {
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .service-block-inner {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .service-block.reverse .service-block-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
  }

  .service-block.reverse .service-block-text {
    order: 2;
  }

  .service-block.reverse .service-block-visual {
    order: 1;
  }

  .service-block-text .section-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .service-block-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .service-block-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 24px 0 32px;
  }

  .service-features li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 8px 0 8px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,58,95,0.07);
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-features li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .service-visual-card {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .svc-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--teal-light);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .service-visual-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .service-visual-card > p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .svc-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .svc-detail {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  .svc-detail:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .svc-detail-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
